  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    COVID-19: Guidance for the safe use of multi-purpose community facilities
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Guidance for those managing community centres, village halls and other community facilities on safely re-opening multi-purpose buildings.  </p>

  </div>
